        "content": "<h3><strong>Grow Fearlessly without Limits.&nbsp;</strong>Don&#39;t let your out of the box digital commerce platform limit you as you grow traffic, expand your product catalog and explore new markets. Virto Commerce allows you to easily add new product configurations, languages, and easily add multiple vendors to your site. Virto Commerce is your ideal&nbsp;<strong>long term</strong><strong>&nbsp;e</strong><strong>commerce partner</strong>, and builds features and functionality specifically for your team as your business needs change.</h3>\n\n<p>With a multitude of changes to B2C and B2B2C ecommerce, especially with an increase in promotions that create complex pricing structures, B2C and B2B2C ecommerce has become more sophisticated in recent years. B2C and B2B2C companies selling large volumes online need to consider their ecommerce platform choices carefully &ndash; risks come with choosing an out-of-the-box platform that fails to grow with your business.<br />\n<br />\nA solution designed for cloud and built on leading Microsoft .NET technology, Virto Commerce&#39;s agile platform is built to handle complicated enterprise digital commerce and is a perfect choice for companies looking to develop a customized .NET ecommerce experience. Leading B2C companies, like&nbsp;<a href=\"/blog/rainbow-sandals-selects-virto-commerce-platform-for-digital-commerce\">Rainbow Sandals</a>, recently chose Virto Commerce to power their online presence.&nbsp;</p>\n",
