                "title": "Built for Cloud",
                "text": "<p>Virto Commerce is designed for the cloud, enabling your business to eliminate infrastructural limitations that hinder business growth. Being based in the cloud offers a multitude of benefits including:&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Seamless upgrades &amp; low maintenance time</li>\n\t<li>Faster time to market</li>\n\t<li>Lower costs &ndash; use money saved to grow your business</li>\n\t<li>Simple deployment (should link to implementation plan docs)</li>\n\t<li>Extensibility</li>\n\t<li>Enhanced security &ndash; ensure customer data is stored safely</li>\n</ul>\n",
