            {
                "image": {
                    "url": "https://vcpro.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/opensource.png"
                },
                "title": "Open Source",
                "text": "<p>Open source allows you limitless access to modify the platform&#39;s code, giving your team endless creative freedom to configure your B2C or B2B2C website to meet your exact specifications. Other benefits that come along with leveraging the power of an open source solution:&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Empower highly customized B2C store fronts by downloading the code and customize the platform yourself.</li>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://virtocommerce.com/contribute-agreement\">Join the Virto Commerce community of developers</a>&nbsp;and implementation partners and tap into their ecommerce expertise.</li>\n</ul>\n",
                "iconStyle": null,
                "url": null
            },
            {
                "image": {
                    "url": "https://vcpro.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/productfind.png"
                },
                "title": "Catalog and Product Information Management",
                "text": "<p>Our platform provides sophisticated catalog management capabilities making it simple and elegant to manage even the most complex B2C product lists. Using Virto Commerce you can:&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Manage digital and physical products using flexible properties structures. Virto Commerce catalog can be configured to handle all your catalog information, or integrated with 3rd party PIM or CMS solutions.</li>\n\t<li>Configure all digital assets to be stored in popular Content Distribution Networks (CDN).</li>\n\t<li>Go Global. Virto Commerce supports multiple catalogs, languages, taxes and storefronts.</li>\n</ul>\n",
                "iconStyle": null,
                "url": null
            },
            {
                "image": {
                    "url": "https://vcpro.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/payment.png"
                },
                "title": "Pricing Tools",
                "text": "<p>Virto Commerce provides a responsive pricing engine ideal for B2C customers. Prices can be personalized in real-time based on audience, campaign, purchase history, geo-location, contracts and other customer-based scenarios.&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Personalized pricing</li>\n\t<li>Price lists</li>\n\t<li>Tiered pricing</li>\n\t<li>Custom currencies (bitcoin, points)</li>\n</ul>\n",
                "iconStyle": null,
