            {
                "image": {
                    "url": "https://vcpro.blob.core.windows.net/blogs/databasearch.png"
                },
                "title": "Multi Tenant",
                "text": "<p>Built to support complex B2C and B2B2C scenarios, Virto Commerce includes capabilities to create solutions for distributors and manufacturers. Create complex org structures, allow vendors to accept orders and customize the look and feel of their storefront. Virto&#39;s software allows you to:&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Create organizations</li>\n\t<li>Vendor store themes and templates</li>\n\t<li>Relate orders to specific vendor/store</li>\n\t<li>Control vendor permissions</li>\n</ul>\n",
